# GOV.UK Wallet

**GOV.UK Wallet** is new way for government departments to exchange documents with users.

**GOV.UK Wallet** allows users to store in a digital format in a mobile app a digital version of letters, entitlements, certificates and other documents created when interacting with a government service.

Users can then share these documents in a digital format with other government service, instead of filling forms and uploading files.

You can [read further documentation about how GOV.UK Wallet works](/how-the-api-works/).

